      <p class="sub__title--renowned title">Mangishi Doll</p>
      <p>
        Mangishi Doll is a Zambian ‘Afro – Eclectic’ Clothing Brand inspired by
        unique style and bold prints. It was established in 2012 by African
        Fashion Designer Kapasa Musonda, who was born and raised in Zambia.
        <p> Mangishi Doll is a cultural and artistic expression of design and style
        through bold patterns and vibrant colors – It is intentionally crafted
        for the Doll that dares to stand out. Mangishi Doll released its first
        official collection in 2014 giving the brand its first online presence.
        </p><p> Since then Mangishi Doll has released seasonal collections that have
        resonated with different people and cultures around the world and has
        dressed celebrities and influencers such as Angela Basset, Susan Kelechi
        Watson and Vonneta Stewart.</p>
      </p>
