      <p class="sub__title--renowned title">THE MD STORE</p>
      <p>
        The MD (Mangishi Doll) Store is a collective of all our MD Clothing
        lines combined. It is a Look Book of all Mangishi Doll pieces which are
        all inspired by unique style & bold prints. We fuse authentic Chitenge
        prints from different parts of Africa as well as cultural, tribal,
        abstract prints and solids from around the world. All MD pieces are
        designed and ethically crafted in Zambia.
      </p>
