      <p>
        The MD Individualist line is a high-end contemporary collection of
        cohesive seasonal pieces inspired by art, culture and individualism. It
        collects authentic prints over a period of time and crafts unique pieces
        into a collection that tell a story. The MD Individualist presents only
        three collections each year and is only available for a limited period
        as the design process is cultivated and uniquely crafted over a period
        of time.
      </p>
